{"tid":83722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蝗 蟲 產 卵！Angelababy 黃 曉 明 G 那 細 菌 香 港 順 產！","createTime":"2017-01-17T03:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T12:47:46.000Z","uid":53178,"like":4,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c77e032ed36fa90e2b61be3c3863cff92a22ed3","tid":83722,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:25:45.000Z","msg":"大陸藝人黃曉明同Angelababy（楊穎）呢對金童玉女，前年5月成婚，揚言要生B，後嚟搵咗中醫為太太調理身體，二人喺默默耕耘下，Baby上年成功懷孕，一索得男，原本預產期係今年農曆新年之後。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》收到風，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>angelababy 已入院順產生男B，黃曉明及雙方家人提前抵港並全程陪伴母子左右，夫婦二人一齊幸福迎接新生命嘅降臨</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n「黃曉明工作室」微博專頁剛才公佈喜訊，留言：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「想與大家分享一個幸福的時刻：今晨Angelababy 於香港順產生子，黃曉明與家人一直全程陪護。AH夫婦共同有了愛的美好延續，從此1+1=3，這大概就是幸福的模樣吧!」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/17/111724_bb8f6afd00424eed232ccd77ffd95f42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F17%2F111724_bb8f6afd00424eed232ccd77ffd95f42.jpg&h=923c4245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZeTzXXdc2ob6hjN6VLmVSCvKjFEUhP4DjENWx7D69ivu?filename=6FcA14W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FcA14W.jpg&h=f8c70f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmejf5q3tDfz6oaZs24JeTcSTTx64oSWBrgiVaRfgCuWfP?filename=ttTf87q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTf87q.jpg&h=0aa25d45&s={SIZE}\" /><strong></strong>"},{"pid":"1061f4096211f131dd23ff245a10c40355786fce","tid":83722,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f146bc5fadb2563ace7ae1448aca60a2c79b9ae4","tid":83722,"uid":76706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g